author: SciShow
description:
In 2021, researchers reported a shocking disappearance in the Bering Sea. Not of people, but of Alaskan snow crabs. And it's taken scientists years to understand how tens of billions of crabs disappeared all at once, so let's take you through the mystery of the disappearing snow crabs!

Hosted by: Savannah Geary (they/them)
